      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: PTP - Procure To Pay
Process Group: PM - Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-050-150 Supplier Selection</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-61F853EF-8073-4138-AC87-C755EA43186A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Communication to supplier will be handled by CM outside of the system (email/meetings) with reasoning for rejection. This will be dependent on larger commodity strategy.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C09CA567-D755-41C7-A4B6-9D3CE3395A1A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Selection decision is not based only on quotes, also includes additional factors such as supplier performance (reports from Bapps supporting decision making)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E700A4D7-AEFE-4AB6-8CC2-570F5E06413B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Description:
Evaluate bids from suppliers and make decision to reject suppliers who submitted responses to the RFQ and were not chosen to provide the item or service. Decision is made based on quote response and other inputs from supplier performance KPIs.
Notify Suppliers who submitted responses to the RFQ and were not chosen to provide the item or service. Communicate to suppliers via e-mail or in meetings reason for rejection and provide feedback for better performance in future sprints.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4F2F8410-033F-4306-8939-98EA0376305B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Nageswaran, Rohan &lt;rohan.nageswaran@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
